<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The sarcophagus [? and the plot] on [?which it stands] belong [ to - - -</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>The restorations printed here are from the standard formula stating the owner(s) of sarcophagi when these are persons of comparatively modest status.</p>
</div>
